        "subject": "PROPOSAL FOR FIXED ASSETS RESPOSIBILITIES",
        "defaultText": "MEMORANDUMTO                :        IT Department\nFROM                :        Human Resources Department\nDATE                :        April 15, 2026\nSUBJECT        :        Proposed Roles and Responsibilities of HR and IT Department\nfor Fixed Assets Management\n________________\nTo strengthen accountability, improve asset monitoring, and ensure proper handling of firm-issued laptops and other IT equipment, we respectfully propose the following division of roles and responsibilities between the Human Resources Department and the IT Department:\n1. Human Resources Department\nThe {department} shall be responsible for the administrative control and employee issuance process of company laptops and related fixed assets, including:\n* Processing and approving asset requisitions based on manpower requests, onboarding, transfers, and role requirements\n* Maintaining coordination with requesting departments regarding laptop allocation needs and reported issues\n* Facilitating the distribution and issuance of laptops to employees\n* Securing signed asset accountability forms / acknowledgments\n* Monitoring employee accountability during movement, resignation, and clearance processes\n* Coordinating with IT for the return and endorsement of assets requiring technical handling\n\n\n2. IT Department\nThe IT Department shall be responsible for the technical management, maintenance, and sourcing support of all IT-related fixed assets, including:\n* Reformatting, system setup, and device preparation prior to deployment\n* Conducting repair, diagnostics, and troubleshooting\n* Coordinating with accredited vendors or service centers for repair and external technical services\n* Providing technical recommendations for laptop specifications, upgrades, replacements, and other IT asset requirements\n* Assessing asset condition upon return and endorsing units for repair, reuse, or disposal\n3) Purpose of the Proposal\nThis proposed structure aims to:\n* Establish clear ownership and accountability\n* Improve turnaround time for laptop requests and repairs\n* Strengthen fixed asset monitoring and documentation\n* Ensure proper technical assessment before issuance and reuse\n* Support more efficient employee onboarding and offboarding processes\n\n\n\n\nProposed By:\n{department}\n\n\nApproved By:\n\n\n{supervisingOfficer}\nManaging Partner\n\n\nACKNOWLEDGMENT AND ASSUMPTION OF RESPONSIBILITY\n\n\nACKNOWLEDGMENT AND ASSUMPTION OF RESPONSIBILITY"
