        "subject": "CERTIFICATE OF EMPLOYMENT (COE)",
        "defaultText": "COE\n\n\nThis is to certify that PATRICIA MAE L. MINIMO is a bonafide employee of Sadsad Tamesis Legal and Accountancy Firm. She was employed with the firm from {startDate} to {responseDeadline} as {position}.\nThis certification is being issued upon the request of Ms. Minimo as proof of her employment with the company.\nIssued on June 10, 2026 at {executionPlace}.\n\n\nReleased By:\n\n\n\n\n{supervisingOfficer}\nHR Officer II\nHuman Resources Department\nSadsad Tamesis Legal and Accountancy Firm\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nProposals\n\n\nRevenue\n\n\nDATE                :        February 03, 2026\nTO                :        Management\nFROM                :        Human Resources Department\nSUBJECT        :        Proposal for {department} Revenue-Generating Initiatives\n\n\n1. BACKGROUND\nIn line with STLAF’s strategic goal to expand services and enhance profitability, the {department} recognizes an opportunity to contribute directly to revenue generation. By leveraging HR expertise in workforce development and regulatory compliance, the department can create value-added services for clients, partner organizations, and internal stakeholders.\n\n\n2. FOCUS AREA\n\n\n1. Training & Development"
