        "subject": "PROPOSAL: EXTERNAL HR TRAINING & ADVISORY REVENUE INITIATIVES",
        "defaultText": "Goal: Offer high-value, paid training programs for external clients\n\n\nINITIATIVE\n\tDESCRIPTION\n\t\n\nCorporate Workshops & Seminars\n\tConduct workshops on workplace compliance, HR best practices, leadership, and productivity for external organizations.\n\t\n\nIn-house and Online Training\n\tDevelop e-learning modules on HR topics: labor laws, employee engagement, recruitment strategies, leadership, and management.\n\t\n\nTarget Market\n* SMEs\n* Corporate clients\nExpected Outcomes:\n* Establish STLAF as a trusted provider of HR training solutions.\n* Generate additional revenue streams through paid workshops and subscriptions.\n* Expand market presence and brand awareness in the HR consulting space.\n\n   2. Compliance & Advisory Services\nGoal: Offer advisory services on HR compliance, labor laws, and risk management for organizations seeking expert guidance.\n\n\nINITIATIVE (Collaborate with {department})\n\tDESCRIPTION\n\tRetrenchment Program Advisory\n\tEnd-to-end guidance in planning and executing retrenchment programs in compliance with DOLE requirements\n\tDue Process Handling (Twin Notice Rule)\n\tAssistance in drafting NTE, administrative hearing documentation, and decision notices\n\tDOLE Compliance Audit\n\tAudit of company policies, 201 files, contracts, and handbook compliance\n\t\n\nTarget Market\n   * SMEs\n   * Startups & Growing Companies\n   * Family-Owned Businesses\n   * Corporate clients\nExpected Outcomes:\n   * Position STLAF as a trusted HR compliance partner.\n   * Reduce legal and operational risks for clients.\n   * Establish recurring revenue opportunities via ongoing advisory contracts.\n\n\n   3. IMPLEMENTATION PLAN\n\n\n   1. Identify Opportunities – Determine client needs and high-demand services in training, development, and HR compliance.\n   2. Develop Offerings – Prepare workshops, online courses, and advisory tools ready for delivery.\n   3. Promote Services – Market programs to target clients and partner organizations.\n   4. Deliver Services – Conduct training and provide advisory support to clients.\n   5. Monitor & Improve – Track client satisfaction, revenue, and service effectiveness; refine offerings as needed.\n\n\nPrepared By:\n\n\n\n\n{supervisingOfficer}\nHR Officer II\n\n\nApproved By:\n\n\n\n\n{supervisingOfficer}\nPartner"
